data.description: Looking for more space and privacy in Northern Colorado? This is it! Magnificent bright and spacious home in desirable Ridge West neighborhood.  This home is ready for outdoor entertaining! Huge back yard backing to open space.  Concrete edging and mature landscape.  Natural privacy with over 40 trees. Don't forget to check out the view of Longs Peak!  Custom built fire pit with four gorgeous built in planters a gardeners dream. This home won't disappoint inside or out. Stunning hand scraped bamboo flooring and soaring ceilings.  New exterior paint. New HVAC system and garage doors.   Garage has ample storage and many built ins. Basement just waiting for final master plan already plumbed and wired. Easy walk to Poudre River Trail. Minutes to downtown Windsor and easy access to I25.  In sought after Poudre school district. No Metro tax. Come take a look before its gone!!
